Wherefore I can see no sense which can agree to the Text, but that which is the ordinary and known sense of the word; 
                  〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
               , that is an Assembly of Elders. In which sense it is also frequently used by ancient writers, whereof, he that will, may read good store of examples in D. Blondelli Apollogia pro sententia Hieronymi. pag: 89 90.
